Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: pve-compose
Architecture: all
Depends: jq, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: pve-container
Suggests: bash-completion
Description: Docker Compose orchestration for Proxmox LXC
 pve-compose transparently orchestrates Docker Compose stacks inside
 LXC containers on Proxmox VE. It creates the LXC, installs Docker,
 configures bind mounts, resolves permissions, and runs docker compose
 - all automatically from a single command.
